tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE token_ownership (
  token_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  owner_id INT NOT NULL,
  timestamp TIMESTAMP NOT NULL
)

CREATE TABLE asset_owners (
  owner_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  first_name VARCHAR(50),
  last_name VARCHAR(50),
  email VARCHAR(50),
  registration_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE TokenTransactions (
    transaction_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    token_id INT,
    sender_id INT,
    receiver_id INT,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE tokens (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    token_name VARCHAR(50),
    token_symbol VARCHAR(10),
    owner_address VARCHAR(100)
)

CREATE TABLE asset_owners (
    owner_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    owner_name VARCHAR(50),
    owner_address VARCHAR(100)
)

CREATE TABLE asset_tokens (
    asset_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    token_id INT,
    quantity INT,
    FOREIGN KEY (token_id) REFERENCES tokens(id)
)

CREATE TABLE regulations (
    regulation_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    regulation_name VARCHAR(100),
    description TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE ownership_logs (
    log_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    asset_id INT,
    owner_id INT,
    FOREIGN KEY (asset_id) REFERENCES asset_tokens(asset_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (owner_id) REFERENCES asset_owners(owner_id)
)
